What is Superior Solutions?
We can show you what you need to know if you’re building a home, or looking to save money on your energy costs. This program can help you if you're looking to save energy and money on one of the following:
Building a new home- Get the knowledge to save money from day one in your new home. We'll show you what you need to consider when building, including: proper insulation, energy-efficient appliances, water heater options, and whether you need a heat pump.
Looking at heat pumps- We can help you find a heat pump dealer wherever you live in Alabama. 
Deciding on a new water heater- We'll show you which option works best for you. Whether you should get a heat pump water heater, an electric tankless water heater, or even a standard electric tank water heater.
 







