Careers














Power Up Your Career
Alabama Power is one of the most respected companies in Alabama. We value our employees because we know they are our most valuable asset. We realize that every job and every employee who performs it is vital to the overall success of our company. There are lots of great reasons to join our team.
 









Alabama Power Jobs













Southern Company Jobs










 
Our People
Diversity is important at Alabama Power. Our customers have diverse perspectives and experiences and it’s important that our employees do, too. We value different outlooks, opinions and ideas because it is the combination of these ingredients that makes a successful work environment. We offer an open and trusting work environment and each day prove that Southern Style – unquestionable trust, superior performance and total commitment – is more than just a phrase, it makes us who we are today.

















Our Promise
More than 100 years ago, one of our founding principles was that the company be developed for the service of Alabama. Today those words still ring true, as our commitment to our state and the customers we serve has grown. Many of our employees serve in the Alabama Power Service Organization (APSO) and their philanthropic efforts don’t stop when they retire, because many continue their commitment to the community with our Energizers group. In addition, the Alabama Power Foundation awards more than 1,300 grants annually with non-ratepayer money.
 
Our Record
Alabama Power is the second largest subsidiary of Southern Company and provides the valuable combination of competitive prices, reliable electricity supply and unparalleled service to 1.4 million homes, businesses and industries in the southern two-thirds of Alabama. For years, we have consistently provided electricity more than 99.9 percent of the time while keeping our prices lower than the national average. Our foundation is solid and we’re still growing to meet tomorrow’s demands.
 
Our future
At Alabama Power, we are always looking for ways to meet new challenges and we know that highly skilled employees hold the key. We are dedicated to giving our employees opportunities to learn, grow and advance in their careers in order to meet the challenges of the future. We need innovative employees who are driven to help us to meet today’s goals for a brighter tomorrow.
Learn more about our exciting career opportunities here.
 








                    
                    
                        Employment Testing Videos
                    
                




