My Power Usage
 
“My Power Usage” from Alabama Power allows you to:

View your daily and monthly usage to learn when you use energy
Learn your projected electric service amount long before you receive your bill.
Receive email alerts when your bill reaches a dollar amount you set.

 


Daily Usage Graph
If it has been at least seven days since your last billing period you will see your projected electric service amount displayed.






















Projected Electric Service
If it has been at least seven days since your last billing period you will see your projected electric service amount displayed.

















Settings and Alerts
To learn about Alerts click on the Set/Manage Alerts area. This feature helps you set a monthly and/or daily energy budget.

















 
To get started:

Click on the “LOGIN” button on the top left of the screen.
Once logged in, eligible customers** will see a link to “My Power Usage” on the left side of the screen.




If you have questions about My Power Usage, please call us at 1-800-990-2726 and press ‘7’ to speak with a specialist about My Power Usage (7:30 a.m. - 5:30 p.m. CST, M-F).
**Some customers may not be eligible for the My Power Usage option due to their participation in other programs, such as time-of- use rates, that do not function with this online tool. If you have questions about your eligibility to participate in My Power Usage, call us at 1-800-990-2726 and press ‘7’ to speak with a specialist, Monday through Friday, 7:30 a.m. - 5:30 p.m.




