Frequently Asked Questions
Questions about Alabama Power? Maybe we can help.


Is online bill pay available for Alabama Power?
You can pay Alabama Power online directly from doxo.  Click to pay Alabama Power on doxo. You can also pay Alabama Power online from their website.  Go to the Alabama Power website at customerservice.southerncompany.com.


What's the login page for Alabama Power?
Sign into your Alabama Power account online at customerservice.southerncompany.com.


I'm not able to login to my online Alabama Power account.  Where can I get help?
The support team for Alabama Power can assist with your account access questions.  View their contact information here: customerservice.southerncompany.com.


Can I access my account or pay Alabama Power from my phone or tablet?
Alabama Power customers with Android mobile phones and tablets can install the Alabama Power for Android app to login to their account via a mobile phone or tablet.  There is no Alabama Power app for iOS available.


How do I contact Alabama Power if I have a question about my account or bill?
Support resources for Alabama Power are available online at customerservice.southerncompany.com. The information listed on that page can help if you need to update your account or have other questions about your bill or statement. Reach Alabama Power via phone at 1-800-245-2244; 1-888-430-5787.


Does Alabama Power go by another name?
No, the primary name is "Alabama Power".


Can I pay Alabama Power with a debit card?
Yes, you can pay Alabama Power with your Discover, MasterCard or Visa Debit Card. Alabama Power is also payable via debit card at their website.


Can I pay Alabama Power with a credit card?
Yes, you can pay Alabama Power with your Discover, MasterCard or Visa Credit Card. Alabama Power is also payable via credit card at their website.


 




